{"tid":1723254,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"入過Poly嘅外援真係辛苦啦","createTime":"2019-11-15T06:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T10:08:52.000Z","uid":220074,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4042db20ecc9888f8be946cde1fd0644b2c38076","tid":1723254,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:44:13.000Z","msg":"非Poly生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連續留守咗幾晚嘅外援<br />\n<br />\n你哋要人幫你哋Poly個個諗都無諗就入去，<br />\n點知就畀人質疑同畀人閪，<br />\n分香港人定分Poly學生重要啲？<br />\n<br />\n仲有班Poly學生去咗邊到，<br />\n會唔會誇張到大嗌左有冇Poly學生隔咁耐先有人認？<br />\n最熟悉Poly環境就係你哋，<br />\n你哋肯出嚟幫手外援唔洗又做多樣嘢。<br />\n<br />\n我哋真心想幫你哋Poly，<br />\n聽到Poly有事要人我哋都即刻過嚟，<br />\n但係我哋係嚟幫手唔係過嚟畀你哋質疑同屌我哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋知錯仲要能改，<br />\n證明返畀班手足知道你哋係有心組織返好，<br />\n唔係乜都要外援受住氣幫你哋做曬呀！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Poly仔證明返畀人睇你哋係做到嘢啦</span>"},{"pid":"8d9b592dd2e34d6b2245dc413843e5e159df165f","tid":1723254,"uid":220074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"唔割"},{"pid":"fb30a20a524a6da857d01c365ba825756733a0d3","tid":1723254,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:45:03.000Z","msg":"[轉守為攻] 將大學要塞化，無限伸展，連結18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0972debd8311df4e151166be98089af5ff28c876","tid":1723254,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"畀我休息完我一定會返嚟繼續幫你哋，<br />\n但係唔想返去仲見到同呢幾日一樣冇進步過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5625e8bd381c7b0a05519f6983bbedd5c6deb94","tid":1723254,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:46:10.000Z","msg":"唔割，但有得揀唔會幫佢地"},{"pid":"6c7bfa9b22d6bb598b93d4156811b10c03dbd387","tid":1723254,"uid":220074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote"